The 'nstat' command explained (SNMT - Simple Network Management Protocol)---> https://www.redhat.com/sysadmin/nstat-command-linux

Splunk troubleshooting network issues ---> https://splunk.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/~phadnett/pages/821731863778/accept+queue+overflow
